==学者==
斯普林菲尔德学院提供40多个专业的学士学位，各种不同领域的硕士学位，以及咨询心理学、物理治疗和体育教育的博士课程。学生与教师的比例是15：1<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://springfield.edu/fast-facts|title=Fast Facts {{!}} Springfield College|website=springfield.edu|language=en|access-date=2017-12-19|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202070733/https://springfield.edu/fast-facts|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

学院分为五所分院:
艺术、科学分院和专业研究分院<ref>{{cite web |url=http://springfield.edu/school-of-arts-sciences-and-professional-studies |title=School of Arts, Sciences, and Professional Studies | Springfield College |publisher=Springfieldcollege.edu |date= |accessdate=2015-09-27 |archive-date=2019-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190622131418/https://springfield.edu/school-of-arts-sciences-and-professional-studies |dead-url=no }}</ref> ；健康、体育和娱乐分院<ref>{{cite web |url=http://springfield.edu/school-of-health-physical-education-and-recreation |title=School of Health, Physical Education, and Recreation | Springfield College |publisher=Springfieldcollege.edu |date= |accessdate=2015-09-27 |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919215522/https://springfield.edu/school-of-health-physical-education-and-recreation |dead-url=no }}</ref> ；健康科学与康复学院<ref>{{cite web |url=http://springfield.edu/school-of-health-sciences-and-rehabilitation-studies |title=School of Health Sciences and Rehabilitation Studies | Springfield College |publisher=Springfieldcollege.edu |date= |accessdate=2015-09-27 |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919215733/https://springfield.edu/school-of-health-sciences-and-rehabilitation-studies |dead-url=no }}</ref>；专业和继续进修学院<ref name="springfieldcollege1">{{cite web |url=http://springfield.edu/school-of-professional-and-continuing-studies |title=School of Professional and Continuing Studies | Springfield College |publisher=Springfieldcollege.edu |date= |accessdate=2015-09-27 |archive-date=2019-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190624092948/https://springfield.edu/school-of-professional-and-continuing-studies |dead-url=no }}</ref>；还有社会工作学院<ref>{{cite web |url=http://springfield.edu/springfield-college-school-of-social-work |title=Springfield College School of Social Work | Springfield College |publisher=Springfield.edu |date= |accessdate=2015-09-27 |archive-date=2019-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612075340/https://springfield.edu/springfield-college-school-of-social-work |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://springfield.edu/academics |title=Academics | Springfield College |publisher=Springfield.edu |date= |accessdate=2015-09-27 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125112603/https://springfield.edu/academics |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

专业的和持续的研究学院提供了人类服务的学位课程，并在全国共有7个卫星校区，以及在马萨诸塞州Springfield的主学院校园。它的校园位于马萨诸塞州的波士顿。得克萨斯州休斯敦的;密尔沃基,威斯康星州;圣Johnsbury,佛蒙特州;佛罗里达州坦帕市;加州南部;斯普林菲尔德,麻萨诸塞州;和特拉华州威尔明顿。<ref name="springfieldcollege1"/>

1988年，{{Link-en|人类服务项目|human services}}来到了春田学院，当时他们是从[[南新罕布什尔大学|南新罕布什尔大学]](当时被称为新罕布什尔大学)获得的<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.snhu.edu/about-us/leadership-and-history/history|title=History|publisher=Southern New Hampshire University|accessdate=July 28, 2017|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104015454/https://www.snhu.edu/about-us/leadership-and-history/history|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

该学院是由新英格兰学校和学院协会认证的。

==校园==
斯普林菲尔德学院由位于马萨诸塞州斯普林菲尔德有一个主校区，另外有八个专业和继续教育学院，分别在[[波士顿|波士顿]]、[[休斯敦|休斯敦]]、 [[密爾瓦基|密爾瓦基]]、[[聖約翰斯堡_(佛蒙特州)|聖約翰斯堡]]、 [[塔斯廷|塔斯廷]]、[[坦帕_(佛羅里達州)|坦帕]]、 和[[威明頓_(德拉瓦州)|威明頓]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.springfield.edu/school-of-professional-and-continuing-studies/campus-locations |title=Campus Locations | Springfield College |publisher=Springfield.edu |accessdate=2015-09-27 |archive-date=2019-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190606003816/https://springfield.edu/school-of-professional-and-continuing-studies/campus-locations |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

主校区占地100英亩（40公顷），包括10个宿舍楼，娱乐和健身设施，扩建和翻新的科学和学术设施，经过翻新的表演艺术中心，以及Richard B. Flynn Campus Union，这里有美食廣場、活动和休息室，以及大学书店<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.springfield.edu/fast-facts |title=Fast Facts | Springfield College |publisher=Springfield.edu |date=2011-06-01 |accessdate=2015-09-27 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202070733/https://springfield.edu/fast-facts |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

斯普林菲尔德学院东校区占地82英亩（33公顷）的森林生态系统，距离主校区约1英里<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.springfield.edu/east-campus |title=East Campus | Springfield College |publisher=Springfield.edu |date= |accessdate=2015-09-27 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128200234/https://springfield.edu/east-campus |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。这个位置提供乡村风格的会议和会议设施，以及户外研究和娱乐的空间。 东校区也是斯普林菲尔德学院儿童发展中心的所在地，该中心为社区教职员工，学生和家庭的儿童提供优质的早期教育服务。

